r! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">#816轉美元!<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">機場拆局最大手牌: 「道歉」+「暗指有鬼搞事」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日既事, 大家都有責任, 有地方係做得唔好, 我地唔同政府/黑警, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地呢一代係識負責任, 係識「道歉」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n喺示威者當中, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">就算有鬼都好, 發生左令大家不愉快既事, 我地都會向大家「道歉」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔小心中左計, <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>做錯唔緊要, 最緊要做番個負責任既人!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然黑警都打左張<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁明既「鬼」牌, 我地都要好好利用番佢</span></strong>, 唔係話所有責任都放喺鬼度, 但至少都八九不離十<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩見到幫手推! 我覺得好重要!<br />\n<br />\n我地 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最大既復仇就係要令今次運動成功, 爭取到五大訴求!!!![</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:24.000Z","msg":"同意!!!!<br />\n<br />\n[幫推]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球道歉運動! </span></strong><br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#團結! Be water! Be humble! 香港人有禮貌!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"813「和你非」有感+未來方向<br />\n已請左人出post 求推 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467311/page/1</a>)"},{"pid":"7d8c4b5982ee1885e694e19ae5e0d52cee0496bd","tid":1467782,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:19.000Z","msg